track_notes: Drive from I-40 to saddle on SE side of A1 then hike up closed jeep trail to top.

This is the route I took to drive up to the start of the hike.  Dirt roads, a bit rocky so high clearance would be best but 4wd probably not required.  It does appear that they close these roads in winter.
track_title: Drive from I-40 to Saddle parking area for A1 Mountain

track_notes: This was a short half-mile hike from the saddle parking area to the top.
In the Winter, the FS closes roads so to activate A-1 Mountain you will need to hike in.  This track is my route.  It is longer but not a difficult hike even when there is snow.
track_title: A1 Hike When the A1 Mountain Road is Closed
